<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>固特超声波清洗机已在</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>全国宝岛眼镜门店上架啦!</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200815/e6038cbd7ea541e6ab56c89715835d72.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<h1 class="ql-align-center"><strong>01 品牌聚力，合作共赢！</strong></h1>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200815/7bf4a28980f24bc9bdd75f30c8edd92d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
